PrecisOrder consenting to an amendment to the VUNTUT GWITCHIN FIRST NATION FINAL AGREEMENT signed on May 29, 1993, whereby the date upon which Her Majesty will be released and indemnified by the Vuntut Gwitchin from any claims associated with two Historic Sites (Lapierre House and Rampart House) will be postponed from May 31, 1996 to May 31, 2000.
